      • plugStubPoolReader

        org.eclipse.keyple.core.seproxy.SeReader plugStubPoolReader(java.lang.String groupReference,
                                                            java.lang.String readerName,
                                                            StubSecureElement se)
        Plug synchronously a new @StubReaderImpl in Pool with groupReference and a StubSE. A READER_CONNECTED event will be raised.
        Parameters:
        groupReference - : group refence of the new stub reader
        readerName - : name of the new stub reader
        se - : insert a se at creation (can be null)
        Returns:
        created StubReader

      • unplugStubPoolReader

        void unplugStubPoolReader(java.lang.String groupReference)
        Unplug synchronously a new reader by groupReference. A READER_DISCONNECTED event will be raised.
        Parameters:
        groupReference - groupReference of the reader to be unplugged
